articles.title: DMART Q2 Result
articles.content:
Sales rises by 10% from 1000 to 1100 Cr (YoY basis).
Net profit rises by 11% from 148 to 164 Cr (YoY basis).

articles.title: DMART Q1 Result
articles.content:
Sales rises by 20% from 1000 to 1200 Cr (YoY basis).
Net profit rises by 10% from 126 to 139 Cr (YoY basis).
